TinaStore - E-commerce Website
TinaStore is a fully responsive and interactive e-commerce website built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Bootstrap. It offers a seamless shopping experience with a well-structured layout, product listing, banners, and a fully functional Bootstrap carousel slider. The project is optimized for different screen sizes, ensuring a great user experience on both desktop and mobile.

🌟 Features
✔️ Responsive Design - Works perfectly on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.
✔️ Product Listings - Displays products dynamically with discounts, ratings, and cart functionality.
✔️ Bootstrap Carousel Slider - Featured promotions displayed in an interactive slider.
✔️ Category Sidebar - Easy navigation through product categories.
✔️ Add to Cart Button - Allows users to add products to their cart easily.
✔️ Wishlist Functionality - Users can favorite products for later.
✔️ Dynamic Banners - Promotional banners that enhance user engagement.
✔️ Multi-Currency & Multi-Language Support (Planned Feature) - Dropdowns for currency and language selection.
✔️ Light/Dark Mode Toggle (Planned Feature) - Improve accessibility and user preference.

🛠️ Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML, CSS, Bootstrap 5
JavaScript: Vanilla JS for dynamic interactions
Icons & Images: SVGs, custom images
Grid & Flexbox: For layout structure

TinaStore/
│── assets/
│   ├── images/        # Product images & banners
│   ├── icons/         # SVG icons for UI elements
│── css/
│   ├── home.css       # Main styles
│── js/
│   ├── Banner.js      # Controls banner behavior
│   ├── Products.js    # Handles product rendering
│── index.html         # Main homepage
│── README.md          # Project documentation (this file)

🎨 Customization
If you want to modify this project:
1️⃣ Modify the Products.js file to add/edit products.
2️⃣ Update Banner.js to change banner text and images.
3️⃣ Modify home.css for styling adjustments.

🐞 Known Issues 
Product Grid : the background of the product card is not well Design
responsive : the website is not responsive on all devices.

🎯 Future Improvements
